Sentencas: Spray coating technique was developed to fabricate dense yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) electrolyte films onto NiO-YSZ porous anode substrates.
Titulo: An anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell with spray-coated yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) electrolyte film

Sentencas: A single fuel cell of Ni-YSZ/YSZ (14.9 mu m)/LSM-YSZ was successfully prepared by spray coating technique.
Titulo: An anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell with spray-coated yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) electrolyte film

Sentencas: The cell was tested using humidified hydrogen as fuel and ambient air as oxidant.
Titulo: An anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell with spray-coated yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) electrolyte film

Sentencas: The cell provided the maximum power densities of 234, 721 and 990 mW/cm(2) at 700, 750 and 800 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: An anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell with spray-coated yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) electrolyte film

Sentencas: The impedance spectra showed that the performance of the cell was controlled by the electrode polarization rather than the resistance of YSZ electrolyte film.
Titulo: An anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell with spray-coated yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) electrolyte film

Sentencas: SEM results revealed that the YSZ film was crack-free, continuous and quite dense.
Titulo: An anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell with spray-coated yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) electrolyte film
